---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 309
  - Title: Phaedrus
    Location: 250
By: Plato
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Symbolism=The Divine Imprint in Manifestation
---
All souls do not easily recall the things of the other world; ...
they are seen through a glass dimly; and there are few who, going to
the images, behold in them the realities, and these only with
difficulty.
